	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.431, and Index, 526, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.305, no. 291, 114 or 113 B.C. Crawford suggests that he was father of no. 62, the consul of 66 B.C., and perhaps the son of the consul of 126. See also M. Stuart, AJA 49, 1945, 226-251.\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7495 .
